Program: Outlook
Title: The Ex-Con Criminal Lawyer
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p036zr45
Last Broadcast Date: Wed 11 Nov 2015
Allan Haber is a successful criminal defence lawyer in New York, but he was once a heroin addict and a prolific drug dealer who has spent more than 15 years behind bars. He spent time in many notorious prisons including Sing Sing and Rikers Island. In many ways prison was a natural progression for Allan who had a very tough start in life. Show less